Version: 3.0-1
Depends: python3-light, python3-urllib, python3-json, python3-math, python3-threading, python3-datetime, python3-re, python3-socket, python3-ssl, python3-gzip, python3-broadlink, python3-schedule, python3-pip
Section: utils
