License: MIT
Description: AI-powered smart AC controller for Broadlink RM series.
 Supports 17 AC brands, dual weather sources (Baidu/QWeather),
 NMC typhoon & NHC hurricane tracking, auto AC shutdown on storm <100km.
 Installs: pip3 install hvac_ir after opkg install (see postinst).
